    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. This driver-focused example boasts a recently serviced Vanos system and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the chassis handles the 333hp output with factory-spec rigidity. Equipped with the M-Variable differential and original staggered Style 67 wheels, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. While the exterior shows minor patina from spirited use, the mechanical fundamentals\u2014including the individual throttle bodies and suspension bushings\u2014are in excellent working order. A true analog masterpiece ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
