    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, stylish daily driver. The exterior retains its original luster, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery shows only light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having received full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of brake pads and a multi-point inspection confirming the engine and transmission are in excellent working order. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a solid, well-cared-for example ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
