    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, providing a direct mechanical connection to the variable M differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS refresh and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering exceptional turn-in precision and mid-corner stability. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains robust with excellent compression and a linear torque curve. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
